                            <comment id="12561190" author="stack" created="Tue, 22 Jan 2008 01:21:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch looks good Stu.  Let me apply it after we make the 0.16 branch.  Currently, only blockers are to be applied (There is to be a vote on 0.16 on the 24th).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12565441" author="bryanduxbury" created="Mon, 4 Feb 2008 18:03:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We&apos;ve been discussing making bloomfilters mandatory on mapfiles. Also, the plan would be to use standard bloomfilters, since we&apos;d only create them when we&apos;re flushing or compacting, and never have to delete from them. In light of that, should we bother with this issue, or just resolve it Won&apos;tFix?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12565449" author="stack" created="Mon, 4 Feb 2008 18:13:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Lets apply the patch.  It fixes the broken counting bloom filter implementation (though this filter type doesn&apos;t look to be directly useful in hbase going forward).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
